WEBVTT

1
00:14:54.269 --> 00:14:56.104
Next.

2
00:14:59.524 --> 00:15:01.359
Miss. next!

3
00:15:01.610 --> 00:15:02.361
Hello.

4
00:15:02.444 --> 00:15:05.071
Please have your passport
open to the right page.

5
00:15:07.532 --> 00:15:08.950
I don't understand.

6
00:16:02.170 --> 00:16:03.170
Thank you.

7
00:17:33.261 --> 00:17:34.262
Hello.

8
00:17:35.513 --> 00:17:37.474
I would like...

9
00:18:25.897 --> 00:18:26.898
Yes?

10
00:18:31.611 --> 00:18:34.739
Did you tell this girl there's
still a spot in the program?

11
00:18:35.406 --> 00:18:37.367
Yes. because there is.

12
00:18:43.164 --> 00:18:44.749
Look here.

13
00:18:47.418 --> 00:18:49.796
This is the old spreadsheet
from last month!

14
00:18:49.879 --> 00:18:53.258
How many times have I told
you. you have to update?

15
00:19:29.502 --> 00:19:30.628
Useless!

16
00:19:32.005 --> 00:19:34.007
I don't want you to
answer the phone anymore.

17
00:35:24.581 --> 00:35:26.041
Good evening!

18
00:35:29.169 --> 00:35:30.170
Password?

19
00:35:32.631 --> 00:35:36.301
I need my bag. please.

20
00:35:36.635 --> 00:35:38.011
No password. no entrance.

21
00:35:42.516 --> 00:35:43.934
No password. no entrance.

22
00:36:17.885 --> 00:36:19.636
Is this your girlfriend?

23
00:36:20.554 --> 00:36:21.680
Yes.

24
00:36:23.181 --> 00:36:24.181
Password?

25
00:36:24.850 --> 00:36:25.850
La Jetée.

26
00:38:17.254 --> 00:38:18.505
C'mon. let's go see.

27
00:38:40.152 --> 00:38:40.903
What's your problem. bitch?

28
00:38:40.986 --> 00:38:42.571
What's going on?

29
00:38:56.668 --> 00:38:57.794
Move. move!

30
00:45:26.891 --> 00:45:28.226
Well. shit.

31
00:45:28.309 --> 00:45:30.395
That's quite a story.

32
00:45:42.115 --> 00:45:45.243
What's the story
with the brother?

33
00:47:51.286 --> 00:47:52.579
Mr. Jules!

34
00:47:52.662 --> 00:47:53.914
One more round. please.

35
00:47:53.997 --> 00:47:55.081
Okay. you got it.
